
• Lunus tulu.
* blue-ASR sky[NOM]
Ⓔ A sky is blue.
[Toaq] Mỉo sa sẻoq da.

• Yus nı yan yu kı ın.
* is_confident_in-ASR thing[NOM] CCI-ACC is_confident_in[OBL] you[NOM] you_know_what-ACC
Ⓔ I am confident that you are confident that you-know-what is the case.

• Reos yor pı mırut kon gapıt.
* has_part-ASR forall-BQZ 1[NOM] cat-SER 4-ACC leg-SER
Ⓔ Every one cat has four legs.
[Toaq] Pảq go tu shỉ kảto sa jỏ shỉaq da.

• Ruyus barut nı da nına dayat.
* are_in_reciprocal_relation-ASR talk-SER me[NOM] PL_UNION is_in_relation_with_me[OBL] is_friend_of-SER
Ⓔ I talk to a friend of mine.
[Toaq] Chẻo kỏy jí roı sa gỏjī pảı da.

• Ruyus barut nı da daya nınım.
* are_in_reciprocal_relation-ASR talk-SER me[NOM] PL_UNION is_friend_of[OBL] me-ACC-CUR.
Ⓔ I talk with a friend of mine.

• Ruyus barut nı da daya wa nın.
* are_in_reciprocal_relation-ASR talk-SER me[NOM] PL_UNION is_friend_of[OBL] CUR me-ACC.
Ⓔ I talk with a friend of mine.

• Pıs ra wayut kaŋ ra mırut.
Ⓔ The dog and the cat are both one in number/numerosity.
[Toaq] Shỉ ke kủnē ru ke kảtō da.

• Nes hayut nı.
Ⓔ I am (the one named after concept) Cloud.
[Toaq] Jẻomī pủao jí da.

• Nes hayut lu nıwa.
Ⓔ It is me who is (the one named after concept) Cloud.
[Toaq] Mỉ pủao meq fỉjī da.
[Toaq] ≈ mỉ pủao ku jí da.

• Nes hayut lu u wa nı.
• Nes hayut lu u nıwım.
Ⓔ It is me who is (the one named after concept) Cloud.

• Nes hayut karur nı.
Ⓔ It is me who is (the one named after concept) Cloud.
[Toaq] Mỉ pủao meyq rủjeo jí da.


